# Firebase / Google Services config — project-specific, contains the
# Firebase project ID and a writeable API key. The key is restricted
# to package-id scope but treating the file as code-committable
# encourages config drift between environments. Keep it out of git;
# CI pipelines drop the right file per environment at build time.
# See aura_final/FIREBASE_SETUP.md for placement.
**/google-services.json
